但是就是耗費置車時間 
單程20-30min
三個單程1-1.5Hr

此全段路線…
在最後一瀑後（上段）
就沒有瀑布了…
後面地形都很簡單好走

踢至漁港後
可以沖洗
1.）廁所沖洗
2.）廟旁邊商店旁可以沖洗</gpxhb:postscript><gpxhb:loadweight>10.0</gpxhb:loadweight><gpxhb:fitnesslevel>1</gpxhb:fitnesslevel><gpxhb:activitytype>others</gpxhb:activitytype><gpxhb:trackimageurl>https://assets.hikingbook.net/users/60w3wu1it91y2jmwdxciziq/a8nscfl2rgscprc5con299w/fa06b738-f44d-4908-a629-928430f95e0e.jpg</gpxhb:trackimageurl><gpxhb:device>Apple iPhone 13 Pro</gpxhb:device><gpxhb:source>Hikingbook</gpxhb:source></extensions></metadata><wpt lat="24.491427415073375" lon="121.831614626685"><ele>276</ele><time>2025-05-17T22:54:40Z</time><name>00 Start</name><cmt>2025-05-18T06:54:40+08:00</cmt><desc>00 Start</desc><src>Hikingbook</src><link href="https://hikingbook.net/hikes/A8NSCfl2RgScpRC5cON299w"><text>Hikingbook</text></link><extensions><gpxhb:weather>Clear</gpxhb:weather><gpxhb:speed>0.000000</gpxhb:speed><gpxhb:course>352.968750</gpxhb:course></extensions></wpt><wpt lat="24.486966333227475" lon="121.83511952878293"><ele>349</ele><time>2025-05-17T23:11:53Z</time><name>01 下切點</name><cmt>2025-05-18T07:11:53+08:00</cmt><desc>01 下切點</desc><src>Hikingbook</src><link href="https://hikingbook.net/hikes/A8NSCfl2RgScpRC5cON299w"><text>Hikingbook</text></link><extensions><gpxhb:weather>Clear</gpxhb:weather><gpxhb:speed>0.227995</gpxhb:speed><gpxhb:course>166.485824</gpxhb:course></extensions></wpt><wpt lat="24.490317728273176" lon="121.83517217910634"><ele>278</ele><time>2025-05-17T23:29:51Z</time><name>02 W1(WT-R-B2-35m)&#xA;</name><cmt>2025-05-18T07:29:51+08:00</cmt><desc>02 W1(WT-R-B2-35m)&#xA;</desc><src>Hikingbook</src><link href="https://hikingbook.net/hikes/A8NSCfl2RgScpRC5cON299w"><text>Hikingbook</text></link><extensions><gpxhb:weather>Clear</gpxhb:weather><gpxhb:speed>0.000000</gpxhb:speed><gpxhb:course>19.986135</gpxhb:course></extensions></wpt><wpt lat="24.490666824062036" lon="121.8351231617226"><ele>253</ele><time>2025-05-18T00:38:22Z</time><name>03 W2(WT-L-B1-3m)</name><cmt>2025-05-18T08:38:22+08:00</cmt><desc>03 W2(WT-L-B1-3m)</desc><src>Hikingbook</src><link